      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. those are good points. i've also heard some people complaining about how this kind of stuff basically just forces gentrification and drives up rent for everyone else in the area. do you think those are actually valid concerns or is that just people being resistant to change?",
      "source": "evaluator"
